、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\nPrayer Meeting for Hong Kong Human Rights and Democracy<br />\n<br />\nThe Letter of No Objection for the meeting (at Chater Garden) and the procession (to US Consulate) has been issued.<br />\n<br />\nThe Meeting<br />\nVenue: Chater Garden, Central<br />\nTime: 13:30-18:30<br />\nSubtheme for each session:<br />\n&quot;Chosen People&quot;, &quot;Praise in Prison&quot;, &quot;Judgement Shall Come&quot;,  &quot;God Bless America&quot;<br />\n<br />\n※※ Signatures for the Declaration of the Hong Kong Human Rights and Democracy will be collected at Chater Garden until 14:30, then be submitted to US Consulate in the procession ※※<br />\n<br />\nThe Procession<br />\nAssemble Point: Chater Garden near Queensway<br />\nAssemble Time: 14:30<br />\nRoute: Start at Chater Garden, go along Garden Road and submit petition letter to US Consulate General at public activity area near bus stop at Lower Albert Road<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1dEdZcy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1dEdZcy.jpg&h=9d27a5d3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MjKYqSz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMjKYqSz.jpg&h=ba976118&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"712c163a3a086548651b006d381b81500e7797e7","tid":1549074,"uid":198455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T08:13:15.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"3f798195015f0b3c886a2d1f0fdc9e8de3076490","tid":1549074,"uid":256309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T08:13:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dd36cab6d84b45ab54e97e8326b3fce8fb67bb6a","tid":1549074,"uid":197005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T08:13:54.000Z","msg":"TUI<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid